        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer520821985" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5698283839910057685">I found this series when I was 11 years old and I couldn&apos;t read them fast enough. Here, more than 10 years later, i&apos;m still so very disappointed in myself for not making all of them my own. They all are enriched with the values of friendship, family, courage, and of course magic. I always envisioned it as a pre-harry potter series, even though I discovered it after I began the HP series.</span>
  <span id="freeText5698283839910057685" style="display:none">I found this series when I was 11 years old and I couldn't read them fast enough. Here, more than 10 years later, i'm still so very disappointed in myself for not making all of them my own. They all are enriched with the values of friendship, family, courage, and of course magic. I always envisioned it as a pre-harry potter series, even though I discovered it after I began the HP series.</span>
